[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    588[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     print(f"  Panel sizes: {df['panel_size'].min()}-{df['panel_size'].max()} patients")
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    589[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
